profile: Established in 2005, Bertrand Plumbing & Heating Inc. has offered premier quality residential and commercial plumbing, heating, ventilation, air conditioning and water treatment services in the Greater Ottawa Area. Our installation and service workmanship has been rewarded with repeat business. We are proud to be a family business and our values of hard work, integrity and honesty continue to be the foundation of our company’s personality. Our talent roster is dedicated to serving our clients through punctuality, professional certifications, project coordination and knowledge. Delivering value is the cornerstone of our business philosophy. Residential and commercial customers count on us to provide fast and reliable service. Our commitment to each job – large or small – remains the same and we insist on getting it right. We have the technical abilities, and quality products (such as Carrier heating and cooling products) to complete any project. When you are looking for residential or commercial plumbing, heating, air or water treatment service solutions in the Greater Ottawa Area, you have contacted the right team!
